        <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Explosive Mines" hidden="false" id="fd81-7c45-3b14-4dce">
          <costs>
            <cost name="pts" typeId="points" value="20"/>
          </costs>
          <constraints>
            <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="parent" shared="true" id="0ff9-1a20-03eb-7bdb" includeChildSelections="false"/>
          </constraints>
          <profiles>
            <profile name="Explosive Mines" typeId="3ce5-e1a1-5b1f-0410" typeName="Wargear" hidden="false" id="037a-c0f8-340e-f9dc">
              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description" typeId="14c0-3a47-fe6d-6563">After an enemy unit finishes a March and is within 9” of this unit, you may roll a D6. If that unit advanced this turn, add 1 to that roll. If that unit finished that March within engagement range of any friendly units, add 1 to that roll. On a 6+, that unit suffers 2D3 Suppression.</characteristic>
              </characteristics>
            </profile>
          </profiles>
        </selectionEntry>
      </selectionEntries>
      <profiles>
        <profile name="Surprise Raids" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="a340-7787-ab25-f443">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit&apos;s End step, if this turn was not your second turn in a row, take another turn.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Tunnelling" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="8ca8-0b5d-e56c-48c9">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit Activates, you may remove it from the battlefield. Then, roll 2D6”. You may Deploy it anywhere on the battlefield surface area within that many inches of any of your other infantry units with Entrenched. If you do, you may select one of your infantry units in reserves. Deploy the selected unit wholly within 6” of this unit outside of the engagement range of enemy models.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
    </selectionEntry>
    <selectionEntry type="unit" import="true" name="Death Korps Platoon Commander" hidden="false" id="03e3-17a9-14d9-64d1">
      <costs>
        <cost name="pts" typeId="points" value="10"/>
      </costs>
      <categoryLinks>
        <categoryLink targetId="205c-3072-067b-d808" id="057d-2517-7bf4-a42e" primary="false" name="Infantry"/>
        <categoryLink targetId="2886-2afd-f65f-9d8e" id="d537-72fa-6b00-87a4" primary="true" name="Leaders"/>
      </categoryLinks>
      <profiles>
        <profile name="Death Korps Platoon Commander" typeId="a706-96eb-fcae-b696" typeName="Unit" hidden="false" id="8f8f-a498-b1f2-ae8b">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="M" typeId="c06e-b1a2-0f87-fe2f">6&quot;</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="T" typeId="a6ad-d820-8495-f5b0">3</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Sv" typeId="9b7f-0dde-683f-6844">5+</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="H" typeId="18e4-1bf9-a9b8-1e50">1</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Rv" typeId="411f-3942-6dc0-7c06">6+</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Death Korps Regimental Orders" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="ab63-5acf-851c-1c9a">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While your other Astra Militarum infantry units are within 24”, gain the following abilities:


Hold The Line: After this unit&apos;s Move step, if it did not Advance this turn, until the End step, each of this unit&apos;s ‘Lasgun’ weapons changes its Tp to Hv and, for each attack made by this unit&apos;s Hv weapons, a Hit Roll of 6 for that attack causes an additional hit.


Over The Top: For each Advance Roll made for this unit, you may reroll that Advance Roll. After this unit makes an Advance Roll, until the End step, it gains the following ability: 


Duty To The Emperor: This unit may select targets for Side Arm weapons even if it did not Activate in engagement range of any enemy units. For each attack this unit makes, a Wound Roll of 6 for that attack causes an additional wound.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Look Out Sir!" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="fa28-44cb-adfd-f4d3">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While one or more of your other ‘DEATH KORPS OF KRIEG’ units are within 6&quot; of and visible to this unit, for each ranged attack that targets this unit, you may change the Sv of this unit to 2+ for that attack.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <infoLinks>
        <infoLink name="Resilient (X)" id="73d9-0b95-c124-7f60" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="253c-c1fa-d29d-d21e">
          <modifiers>
